---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Projects | Daniel Castleberry" description="A showcase of my cybersecurity projects.">
    <h1>Projects</h1>
    <p>This is where I apply my skills to solve problems, learn new technologies, and build things. My blog's CTF write-ups are my ongoing micro-projects.</p>

    <div class="project-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>Cybersecurity Homelab</h2>
        <p>A multi-segmented virtual network environment for safely conducting malware analysis, practicing penetration testing, and simulating network defense scenarios. This project demonstrates my hands-on skills in networking, virtualization, and systems administration.</p>
        <a href="/homelab" class="cta-secondary">View Lab Details</a>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>CTF Write-ups & Security Research</h2>
        <p>I regularly participate in Capture The Flag competitions to sharpen my problem-solving and technical skills. Each write-up is a detailed project report on how I identified, exploited, and documented a system's vulnerabilities.</p>
        <a href="/blog" class="cta-secondary">Read Write-ups</a>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
<style>
    .project-card {
        background: var(--glass-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: var(--accent-color);
    }
    .cta-secondary {
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        background-color: transparent;
        color: var(--accent-color);
        border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .cta-secondary:hover {
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
        color: var(--bg-color);
    }
</style>